188
00:12:34,323 --> 00:12:35,926
Hawkeyes,
ingat wajah ini.

189
00:12:36,054 --> 00:12:37,432
Jangan asal tembak.

190
00:12:38,902 --> 00:12:40,369
Jangan cemaskan aku.

191
00:12:40,497 --> 00:12:41,458
Siapa dia?

192
00:12:41,586 --> 00:12:42,932
Kau lupa.

193
00:12:43,060 --> 00:12:44,854
