207
00:13:13,018 --> 00:13:14,096
Apa kabar, Marsh?

208
00:13:14,223 --> 00:13:15,407
Bagaimana keadaan mereka?

209
00:13:16,017 --> 00:13:17,298
Mulai memahami keadaan.

210
00:13:18,099 --> 00:13:19,703
Selamat bergabung.

211
00:13:19,831 --> 00:13:21,690
