213
00:13:23,792 --> 00:13:26,035
Perkenalkan Suharato Rahmat.

214
00:13:26,163 --> 00:13:28,278
Mantan warga negara Inggris
yang jadi pedagang senjata.

215
00:13:28,407 --> 00:13:30,008
