706
00:51:43,955 --> 00:51:45,973
Jangan bergerak dan balik badan.

707
00:51:46,423 --> 00:51:47,256
Pelan-pelan.

708
00:51:47,384 --> 00:51:48,920
Yang mana, kawan?

709
00:51:49,049 --> 00:51:51,891
Jangan bergerak
