00:51:52,595 --> 00:51:54,006
Balik badan.

711
00:51:54,133 --> 00:51:55,127
Perlahan-lahan.

712
00:52:00,051 --> 00:52:01,876
Astaga!

713
00:52:02,004 --> 00:52:04,792
Colin, kau mengejutkanku,
