716
00:52:10,132 --> 00:52:12,247
Kau bisa tak sengaja menembak.

717
00:52:25,394 --> 00:52:26,962
Tepat waktu, Tn. Marsh.

718
00:52:30,904 --> 00:52:31,769
Marsh?

719
00:52:31,897 --> 00:52:33,556
Misi ini adalah jebakan.

720
00:52:33,684 --> 00:52:35,442
Seseorang membocorkan informasi kita.

721
00:52:39,929 --> 00:52:41,588
Tuntutanku sederhana.

722
00:52:42,324 --> 00:52:43,827
Pertukaran tahanan.

723
00:52:43,954 --> 00:52:46,678
Aku ingin tawananmu,
Phen Lyong Bai.

