758
00:55:59,382 --> 00:56:01,681
Paithoon dan Takk
tidak merespons.

759
00:56:04,177 --> 00:56:06,259
Kamar 657, dek B.

760
00:56:06,388 --> 00:56:08,022
Terima kasih.

761
00:56:12,785 --> 00:56:14,355
Gunner.

762
00:56:14,483 --> 00:56:16,949
Takk?
