869
01:06:27,819 --> 01:06:30,253
Maaf.

870
01:06:31,082 --> 01:06:32,713
Aku merasa sedikit dimanfaatkan.

871
01:06:39,372 --> 01:06:40,970
Baik, ayo.

872
